00:07:02.282 --> 00:07:05.079
was what the circuit did
when nothing was forcing it.

00:07:05.079 --> 00:07:07.483
We just put in some initial
energy, some charge,

00:07:07.483 --> 00:07:09.014
and let the circuit sort of sag

00:07:09.014 --> 00:07:10.873
toward wherever it was going.

00:07:10.873 --> 00:07:12.653
That's the natural response.

00:07:12.653 --> 00:07:14.695
The forced response is going to be

00:07:14.695 --> 00:07:17.982
what the input source
forces the circuit to do.

00:07:17.982 --> 00:07:20.200
And when we take those two
things and add them together

00:07:20.200 --> 00:07:22.853
we'll get what the circuit
is going to do altogether.

00:07:22.853 --> 00:07:27.020
And this is another good
