00:07:33.881 --> 00:07:36.367
We're going to take two
things that the circuit does

00:07:36.367 --> 00:07:38.192
and analyze them separately

00:07:38.192 --> 00:07:40.645
and then add them
together, superimpose them,

00:07:40.645 --> 00:07:42.812
to get the total response.

00:07:43.869 --> 00:07:45.892
So they way we do this, the strategy is

00:07:45.892 --> 00:07:47.975
for the natural response,

00:07:49.707 --> 00:07:53.340
basically we take for
