00:08:13.934 --> 00:08:16.926
And when we take the forced response

00:08:16.926 --> 00:08:18.093
we do the opposite, what we do is

00:08:18.093 --> 00:08:20.146
we set the initial conditions to zero,

00:08:20.146 --> 00:08:21.890
simplify the circuit down

00:08:21.890 --> 00:08:24.039
and we use the inputs that
are actually applying.

00:08:24.039 --> 00:08:27.084
In this case, it was V of S.

00:08:27.084 --> 00:08:29.938
And then you get the total response,

00:08:29.938 --> 00:08:32.291
