which is Q and V not,

00:08:42.749 --> 00:08:46.057
and you get V S, all together.

00:08:46.057 --> 00:08:47.503
So that's our strategy.

00:08:47.503 --> 00:08:50.185
And by turning it into
two simpler problems,

00:08:50.185 --> 00:08:52.723
